name: Highschool Life - Wikihow Gam Jam 2020 (Unfinished)
description: The quirk with this game jam was that you went to a random Wikihow page and that was your theme. My page was https://www.wikihow.com/Scrapbook, and so I mdecided to make a game about putting your memories from high school into a scrapbook. Sadly, this was my very first game I actually tried to finish, and so I ran into some issues I hadn't ran into before, making it so that I wasn't able to finish. This is a very basic version that has no endstate, and I may come back to it later, but I really enjoyed the concept and the art I made, so here it is!
